---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layout/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';

const breadcrumbItems = [
  { href: '/', label: 'Home' },
  { href: '/what-we-do', label: 'What We Do' },
  { href: '/what-we-do/projects', label: 'Projects' },
  { href: '', label: 'Empowering Teenagers' },
];
---

<BaseLayout title='Empowering Teenagers'>
  <Breadcrumb items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <section class='py-13'>
    <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8'>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8'>
        <!-- Main blog content -->
        <main class='md:col-span-7 lg:col-span-8'>
          <h1 class='text-4xl hist font-bold mb-4'>Empowering Teenagers:</h1>
          <p class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-6'>
            A Vibrant Day of Learning and Inspiration in Shauri Yako Estate.
          </p>

          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            In the heart of Homa Bay Town, the lively neighborhood of Shauri
            Yako Estate burst into a celebration of youth, knowledge, and
            empowerment as the organization hosted a transformative day tailored
            for teenagers and adolescents. Designed to be both engaging and
            impactful, the event addressed critical challenges facing the
            youth—ranging from drug abuse and teenage pregnancy to school
            dropout, environmental conservation, and sexual and reproductive
            health.
          </p>

          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            The day began with high energy and warm welcomes from ICAN
            volunteers, creating an atmosphere of excitement and inclusivity.
            Icebreaker games helped dissolve barriers, encouraging laughter and
            new friendships while setting a positive tone for the day ahead.
          </p>

          <div class='my-6'>
            <img
              src='/img/CD2-min.jpg'
              alt='Partnership success'
              class='rounded w-full object-cover'
            />
          </div>

          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            Beyond the learning, the event celebrated creativity and physical
            well-being through a vibrant mix of recreational activities. Sports
            tournaments, dance-offs, and talent showcases allowed teenagers to
            shine, building confidence and camaraderie while highlighting the
            rich pool of talent within the community.
          </p>
          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            As the sun set over Shauri Yako Estate, the day concluded with a
            spirited community celebration. Teenagers, volunteers, and residents
            came together to reflect, celebrate, and affirm the strength of
            their shared experiences. It was a powerful reminder that change
            begins with connection—and that young people, when supported and
            heard, can shape a brighter future.
          </p>
          <p class='mb-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed'>
            Thanks to the unwavering efforts of ICAN and the enthusiastic
            participation of local youth, the event was more than just a day of
            fun—it was a launchpad for growth, awareness, and positive action.
            The empowered teenagers of Shauri Yako Estate now carry with them
            not just memories, but a renewed sense of confidence, purpose, and
            hope.
          </p>
        </main>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class='md:col-span-5 lg:col-span-4 space-y-6 mt-8 md:mt-0'>
          <div class='bg-gray-100 rounded overflow-hidden shadow'>
            <img
              src='/img/CD1-min.jpg'
              alt='Partnership success'
              class='w-full object-cover'
            />
          </div>
          
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
